# World State Testing & Validation Strategy

## Test Case Matrix
- State updates (all domains)
- Event emission/handling (sync & async)
- Persistence (save/load, partial updates)
- Error handling (invalid updates, event failures)
- Mod/AI API usage

## Mock Data & Test Harness
- Use mock world state for isolated tests
- Simulate event flows and state changes
- Provide test harness for mods/AI agents

## Continuous Integration
- Run all tests on PRs/commits
- Require coverage for core state/event logic
- Regression tests for all integrated systems

## Coverage Goals
- 90%+ for core world state/event code
- 100% for API validation and security checks

## Versioning & Regression
- Track test coverage for all state/event schema versions
- Add regression tests for all migrations and breaking changes
- Document test results and failures in this artifact

